<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Acreditación</title>

  <style>
    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    body{
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b);
      color:white;
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:center;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .contenedor{
      text-align:center;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding:50px;
      border-radius:18px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      width:90%;
      max-width:700px;
    }

    h1{
      font-size:56px;
      margin-bottom:15px;
      letter-spacing:1px;
    }

    p{
      font-size:20px;
      opacity:0.9;
      margin-bottom:30px;
    }

    .boton{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:14px 28px;
      background:#2563eb;
      color:white;
      text-decoration:none;
      border-radius:10px;
      font-weight:bold;
      transition:0.3s;
    }

    .boton:hover{
      background:#1d4ed8;
      transform:translateY(-3px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="contenedor">
    <h1>Acreditación</h1>
    <p>Plataforma web de apoyo a la gestión institucional y aseguramiento de la calidad.</p>
    <a href="#" class="boton">Comenzar</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
